#### Major tools used for discovering devices on the same network ####

1) netdiscover :
	usage : netdiscover -r <target-ip>

2) nmap : zenmap (gui for nmap)
	usage : 1) ping scan (basic info about all devices connected on the network)
		   nmap -sn <target-ip>
		2) quick scan (basic info with open ports )
		   nmap -T4 -F <target-ip>